<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="51">
The description of bracts and bracteoles is insufficient because most of the bracts and bracteoles had been shed. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gardner &amp; Champ" authorityYear="1849" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma oblongifolium" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolium">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma oblongifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C. Y. Wu" authorityYear="1977" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma lenticellatum" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lenticellatum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma lenticellatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have 3-bracteate flowers (
<bibRefCitation author="Gardner, G" journalOrPublisher="Hooker's Journal of Botany and Kew Garden Miscellany London" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="308 - 320" refId="B4" refString="Gardner, G, 1849. Descriptions of some new genera and species of plants, collected in the island of Hong Kong. Hooker's Journal of Botany and Kew Garden Miscellany London 1: 308 - 320" title="Descriptions of some new genera and species of plants, collected in the island of Hong Kong." volume="1" year="1849">Gardner 1849</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Hsieh, CF" journalOrPublisher="Flora of Taiwan" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" pagination="1 - 9" refId="B7" refString="Hsieh, CF, 1993. Hamamelidaceae. Flora of Taiwan vol. 3: 1 - 9" title="Hamamelidaceae." volume="vol. 3" year="1993">Hsieh 1993</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Wu, CY" journalOrPublisher="Flora Yunnanica" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" pagination="130 - 132" refId="B17" refString="Wu, CY, 1977. Eustigma lenticellatum C.Y.Wu. Flora Yunnanica vol. 1: 130 - 132" title="Eustigma lenticellatum C. Y. Wu." volume="vol. 1" year="1977">Wu 1977</bibRefCitation>
), while 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Oliv" authorityYear="1891" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma balansae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="balansae">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma balansae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has 2-bracteate flowers (
<bibRefCitation author="Oliver, D" journalOrPublisher="Hooker's Icones Plantarum; or Figures, with brief Descriptive Characters and Remarks of New or Rare Plants" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" refId="B12" refString="Oliver, D, 1891. Eustigma balansae Oliv. Hooker's Icones Plantarum; or Figures, with brief Descriptive Characters and Remarks of New or Rare Plants vol. 20" title="Eustigma balansae Oliv." volume="vol. 20" year="1891">Oliver 1891</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Tardieu, ML" journalOrPublisher="Flore du Cambodge, du Laos et du Vietnam" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" pagination="106 - 107" refId="B16" refString="Tardieu, ML, 1965. Eustigma. Flore du Cambodge, du Laos et du Vietnam vol. 4: 106 - 107" title="Eustigma." volume="vol. 4" year="1965">Tardieu 1965</bibRefCitation>
). This could be a key trait to distinguish between species. Further collections of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. Toyama, Tagane &amp; V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma honbaense" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="honbaense">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma honbaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are needed.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="51">
The 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">matK</emphasis>
sequences between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. Toyama, Tagane &amp; V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma honbaense" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="honbaense">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma honbaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gardner &amp; Champ" authorityYear="1849" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma oblongifolium" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolium">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma oblongifolium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(AF013043) differ in 6 bases of the 781 total. The 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">rbcL</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">matK</emphasis>
sequences between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. Toyama, Tagane &amp; V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma honbaense" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="honbaense">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma honbaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Oliv" authorityYear="1891" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Hamamelidaceae" genus="Eustigma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Eustigma balansae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="4" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="balansae">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">Eustigma balansae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">rbcL</emphasis>
: HQ415214, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="51">matK</emphasis>
: HQ415379) differ in 1 base of the 517 total and 5 bases of the 761 total, respectively.
</paragraph>
